query:
query getWardrobeMaterials($categoryId: Int!, $subCategoryId: Int!, $moduleId: Int!, $cityId: Int!, $finishId: String, $xpDoowupInHL: Boolean!, $orderProfileType: OrderProfileType!, $priceVersion: Int!, $paymentStage: Int, $projectCreationDate: String, $isElemental: Boolean, $elementalType: String, $orderBookingDate: String) {
  getWardrobeMaterial(categoryId: $categoryId, subCategoryId: $subCategoryId, moduleId: $moduleId, cityId: $cityId, finishId: $finishId, xpDoowupInHL: $xpDoowupInHL, orderProfileType: $orderProfileType, priceVersion: $priceVersion, paymentStage: $paymentStage, projectCreationDate: $projectCreationDate, isElemental: $isElemental, elementalType: $elementalType, orderBookingDate: $orderBookingDate) {
    woodenMaterials {
      shutterCoreCode
      shutterCoreName
      shutterFinishCode
      shutterFinishName
      orderProfileTypes
      shutterDesignType
      shutterFinishType
      shutterFinishCategory
      shutterColour {
        finishGroup
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    frameMaterials {
      shutterCoreCode
      shutterCoreName
      shutterFinishCode
      shutterFinishName
      orderProfileTypes
      shutterDesignType
      shutterFinishCategory
      __typename
    }
    visibleSideMaterials {
      shutterCoreCode
      shutterCoreName
      shutterFinishCode
      shutterFinishName
      shutterDesignType
      shutterFinishCategory
      orderProfileTypes
      __typename
    }
    multiPartShutterMaterials {
      shutterFinishCode
      shutterFinishName
      shutterCoreName
      shutterCoreCode
      shutterDesignType
      shutterFinishCategory
      minWidth
      maxWidth
      minHeight
      maxHeight
      __typename
    }
    glassMaterials {
      type
      materialId
      isMirror
      finishId
      __typename
    }
    infillShutterMaterial {
      shutterName
      shutterId
      infillMaterials {
        shutterCoreCode
        shutterCoreName
        shutterFinishCode
        shutterFinishName
        shutterCategory
        orderProfileTypes
        shutterDesignType
        shutterFinishType
        shutterFinishCategory
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
